{"tid":1388892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點先叫做合適既家用？","createTime":"2019-07-30T19:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:54:51.000Z","uid":220775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eda896b6139cb47c917da7c919868524eeaae88c","tid":1388892,"uid":220775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:12:59.000Z","msg":"每日都離不開家用問題<br />\n其實真係一個人交租食飯車錢都好勉強<br />\n佢既數字同我實際交出既數字<br />\n完全傾唔掂<br />\n應該話直情冇傾既餘地<br />\n一唔順意又唔聽電話<br />\n成個關係就建立係<br />\n有冇家用同家用幾多之上<br />\n真係好攰<br />\n<br />\n到底點先平衡到？<br />\n做香港人真係好慘<br />\n捱通賬、捱貴樓、仲要捱出街俾人打<br />\n繼續有返工冇收工<br />\n入同出不成正比"},{"pid":"c1ed8b62ee0ad3af8a978f2f099c06dda5deeaeb","tid":1388892,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:16:19.000Z","msg":"點解要比？"},{"pid":"1010753ad4d744d2b07c27cef65d0d1b9b0b39b5","tid":1388892,"uid":220775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1ed8b62ee0ad3af8a978f2f099c06dda5deeaeb","tid":1388892,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:16:19.000Z","msg":"點解要比？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:54:51.000Z","msg":"因為唔俾就不孝囉<br />\n但俾又好困難"}]}